Processing Status Choices

Processing Status

The following are the processing status choices that are available in the DRAW Client.

  1. SERIES_SEPARATED: The series has been separated into individual studies.

  2. TEMPLATE_NOT_MATCHED: The series does not match any of the autosegmentation templates.

  3. MULTIPLE_TEMPLATES_MATCHED: The series matches multiple autosegmentation templates.

  4. MULTIPLE_TEMPLATES_FOUND: The series matches multiple autosegmentation templates.

  5. NO_TEMPLATE_FOUND: The series does not match any of the autosegmentation templates.

  6. READY_FOR_DEIDENTIFICATION: The series is ready for deidentification.

  7. DEIDENTIFIED: The series has been deidentified.

  8. DEIDENTIFICATION_FAILED: The series deidentification failed.

  9. RTSTRUCT_EXPORT_FAILED: The RTStruct export failed.

  10. RTSTRUCT_EXPORTED: The RTStruct has been exported.

  11. ERROR: An error occurred during the processing of the series.

Series State Choices

The following are the series state choices that are available in the DRAW Client.

  1. PROCESSING: The series is being processed.

  2. UNPROCESSED: The series has not been processed as the autosegmentation templates are not matched.

  3. COMPLETE: The series has been processed completely.

  4. FAILED: The series processing failed. Please see the Series Processing Logs for more details.
